en Sie bitte unsere \u00c4rzte:\n[Kontakt](http://acamed.ch/arzt-duebendorf/kontakt-duebendorf/)\nWeitere Informationen finden Sie auch unter :\n[http://www.chinamed.com/libraries.files/Newsletter_10.pdf](http://www.chinamed.com/libraries.files/Newsletter_10.pdf)", "language": null, "image": "https://acamed.ch/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/chinesische-kr\u00e4utertherapie-1.png", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["#main", "https://acamed.ch/", "https://acamed.ch/", "https://acamed.ch/standorte/", "https://acamed.ch/arzt-medizinzentrum-duebendorf/", "https://acamed.ch/arztpraxis-uster/", "https://acamed.ch/aerztezentrum-binz/", "https://acamed.ch/aerztezentrum-zuerich-luchswiesen/", "https://acamed.ch/arztpraxis-wangen/", "https://acamed.ch/medizinisches-angebot/", "https://acamed.ch/hausarzt/", "https://acamed.ch/gynaekologie-frauenarzt/", "https://acamed.ch/chinesische-arzneimitteltherapie/", "https://acamed.ch/akupunktur-tcm-dubendorf-uster/", "https://acamed.ch/akupunktur-tcm-dubendorf-uster/", "https://acamed.ch/arzt-medizinzentrum-duebendorf/augenakupunktur/", "https://acamed.ch/arzt-medizinzentrum-duebendorf/long-covid-tcm-spezialsprechstunde/", "https://acamed.ch/akupunktur-tcm-schwangerschaft/", "https://acamed.ch/kopfschmerzen-und-migraene-akupunktur-tcm-als-wirksame-therapie/", "https://acamed.ch/kosmetische-akupunktur/", "https://acamed.ch/arzt-medizinzentrum-duebendorf/psychotherapie-psychologie-psychiatrie/", "https://acamed.ch/diabetes-chronic-care/", "https://acamed.ch/diabetes-chronic-care/", "https://acamed.ch/diabetes/", "https://acamed.ch/reisemedizin-impfung/", "https://acamed.ch/arzt-medizinzentrum-duebendorf/ernaehrungsberatung/", "https://acamed.ch/corporatehealth/", "https://acamed.ch/aesthetische-medizin-botulinum-hyaluron-faltenbehandlung-dubendorf-schwamendingen/", "https://acamed.ch/uber-uns/", "https://acamed.ch/uber-uns/", "https://acamed.ch/team/", "https://acamed.ch/lehrarztpraxis/", "https://acamed.ch/gesund-fit-blog/", "https: